name: df-lt
params: setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, setvar s3
body: |- wceq(cltrr, copab(s0, s1, wa(wa(wcel(cv(s0), cr), wcel(cv(s1), cr)), wex(s2, wex(s3, wa(wa(wceq(cv(s0), cop(cv(s2), c0r)), wceq(cv(s1), cop(cv(s3), c0r))), wbr(cv(s2), cltr, cv(s3))))))))
comment: Define 'less than' on the real subset of complex numbers. Proofs should typically use ` < ` instead; see ~ df-ltxr . (Contributed by NM, 22-Feb-1996.) (New usage is discouraged.)
